  },
});
```

## üöÄ **Setup Instructions**

1. **Initialize project:**
```bash
npx create-expo-app NewsArticles --template blank
cd NewsArticles
```

2. **Install dependencies:**
```bash
npm install @react-navigation/native @react-navigation/native-stack
npm install react-native-screens react-native-safe-area-context
npm install @react-native-async-storage/async-storage
npm install @reduxjs/toolkit react-redux
npm install react-native-responsive-screen react-native-reanimated
npm install react-native-vector-icons
npm install expo-constants expo-file-system
```

3. **Create all the files** with the contents above

4. **Run the app:**
```bash
npm start
```

